page.content:
This survey was completed by the pupils of St. Winifred's School.
Teachers involved were Mrs Hawkins and Mr Medway.
Parish Council Work - C. Prince, J. Sloane, S. Latham and J. Crowther. Amenities - B. Yeates, D. Dell, J. Calais and L. Jenvey. Bartley Middle School - G. Bailey, J. Bailey, G. Bestic, M. Collett, Z. Comaish, D. Edwards, K. Freemantle, M. Hawkins, J. Keel, H. Kimber, S. Kotecha, E. Lacey, V.Mehta, E. Partridge, P.Rai, G.Salter, A. Stockton-Chalk, N. Smith, V. Thompson, A. Weeks, Susan and Sarah White. The Farm Visit and Golden Hayes by members of Form Two. Computing by Marcus Hebbes and Jayne Hilditch.
